import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; function Home() { const [text, setText] = useState(''); const welcomeText = 'Hello'; const typingDelay = 125; // Delay between each character typing const erasingDelay = 125; // Delay between erasing each character const newTextDelay = 2000; // Delay before starting the next cycle useEffect(() => { const handleTyping = () => { setText((prevText) => { if (prevText.length < welcomeText.length) { return welcomeText.slice(0, prevText.length + 1); } else { return prevText; } }); }; const handleErasing = () => { setText((prevText) => { if (prevText.length > 0) { return welcomeText.slice(0, prevText.length - 1); } else { return prevText; } }); }; let timer = setTimeout(handleTyping, typingDelay); setTimeout(() => { clearTimeout(timer); timer = setTimeout(handleErasing, erasingDelay); }, newTextDelay); return () => clearTimeout(timer); }, [text]); const styles = { background: 'black', width: '100vw', height: '100vh', display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center', color: 'white', fontSize: '3rem', }; const responsiveStyles = { fontSize: '2rem', }; return (
